item.dc:creator: @Jaegon Jaegon
item.description:
@Jaegon wrote:

You need:

  1. Jdk 7u5
  2. Portforward
  3. No-Ip
  4. Firewall ( Open Ports in Windows Firewall )
  5. Client & Source
  6. Run Source

If you need more help go to:

http://rsps-help.weebly.com/index.html
